title: Tired of bad team :/
body:
> I come to gank mid for Annie
> I use Rengar ult to pounce onto Syndra 
> "Don't ult Annie!"
> *Annie ult!*
> "Annie, no! Get outa there! Get outa -"
> *Syndra picks up Tibbers and throws it at us*
> *Annie dies*
> Annie are you okay?
> are you okay?
> are you okay, Annie?

Please nerf this :(
